One of the most powerful weapons, found in a hidden location.

'''Location:'''
* In the Sea Cave
* Hidden in a specific treasure chest
* Requires boat access

=== Erdrick's Helmet ===
The helmet from Erdrick's equipment set.

'''Location:'''
* Tower south of Moonbrooke
* In a hidden room

=== Erdrick's Armor ===
The best armor in the game.

'''Location:'''
* Found in Hargon's Castle
* In a treasure room

=== Charm of Rubiss ===
Essential item for confronting Hargon.

'''Location:'''
* Rubiss Tower
* Given after completing the tower's puzzle

== Hidden Characters ==

=== Roge Fastfinger ===
