== Secret Mechanics ==

=== Party Death ===
When a party member dies:
* They can be revived at churches
* Gold is halved on total party death
* Cannock and Moonbrooke join at fixed levels

=== Lottery Tickets ===
Some towns have lottery systems:
* Purchase tickets for a chance at items
* Rare items possible from jackpots

== Hidden Locations ==

=== Rhone Plateau ===
The final area with difficult enemies:
* Accessible via cave after obtaining all crests
* Contains some of the game's hardest random encounters
* Multiple save points recommended

=== Rubiss Tower ===
Optional but essential dungeon:
* Complex floor navigation
* Required for Charm of Rubiss
* Difficult enemies within

